`c:\Users\jmaca\OneDrive\Desktop\Cursor builds\Socrates\`

## Site Files (all in `socrates/` subfolder)
- `socrates/index.html` — Homepage (hero, categories, trending tools, how it works)
- `socrates/marketplace.html` — Browse and run AI tools
- `socrates/dashboard.html` — Builder analytics dashboard
- `socrates/publish.html` — Publish your own AI tools
- `socrates/pricing.html` — Pricing plans
- `socrates/about.html` — Mission, team, values, press, careers
