## Design System
- **Dark bg:** `#07070e` / `#0e0e1c` / `#14142a`
- **Gold accent:** `#c9a84c` (primary brand color)
- **Purple accent:** `#7c3aed`
- **Fonts:** Inter (body) + Playfair Display (headings)
- Animated starfield canvas on homepage
- All pages share the same nav and footer pattern

## Key Platform Concepts
- **4 tool types:** Prompt Apps, AI Agents, Connectors, Fine-Tuned Models
- **Revenue share:** Builders keep 80%, Socrates keeps 20%
- **Trending algorithm:** Ranks by retention + satisfaction, not clicks
- **Fork attribution:** Builders earn upstream when tools are remixed
- **Stats:** 48K tools, 2.1M monthly users, 92K builders, $4.2M paid out

